doc_summary_long: A high school freshman barred from classes for dyeing her hair red may soon be back in the classroom. 'Thursday I painted my hair red and then they didn't let me go in class,' she says. New rules at the West Side charter school say 'artificial red hair of any kind is not permitted.'So, the high school freshman used mahogany brown on the red dye to tone it down.
doc_summary_short: A high school freshman barred from classes for dyeing her hair red may soon be back in the classroom.
doc_title: Student Disciplined As School Splits Hairs About What Kind Of Red Dye Is OK
